hael W. Watkins|Michael Watkins]]\n|Vince Gilligan & John Shiban & Frank Spotnitz\n|December 6, 1998\n|6ABX05\n|17.01\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |128\n|6\n|11\n|\"[[Two Fathers]]\"\n|Kim Manners\n|Chris Carter & Frank Spotnitz\n|February 7, 1999\n|6ABX11\n|18.81\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |129\n|6\n|12\n|\"[[One Son]]\"\n|Rob Bowman\n|Chris Carter & Frank Spotnitz\n|February 14, 1999\n|6ABX12\n|16.57\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |135\n|6\n|18\n|\"[[Milagro (The X-Files)|Milagro]]\"\n|Kim Manners\n|''Story by''\u200a: John Shiban & Frank Spotnitz \n''Teleplay by''\u200a: Chris Carter\n|April 18, 1999\n|6ABX18\n|15.2\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |138\n|6\n|21\n|\"[[Field Trip (The X-Files)|Field Trip]]\"\n|Kim Manners\n|''Story by''\u200a: Frank Spotnitz \n''Teleplay by''\u200a: John Shiban & Vince Gilligan\n|May 9, 1999\n|6ABX21\n|15.38\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |139\n|6\n|22\n|\"[[Biogenesis (The X-Files)|Biogenesis]]\"\n|Rob Bowman\n|Chris Carter & Frank Spotnitz\n|May 16, 1999\n|6ABX22\n|15.86\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |143\n|7\n|4\n|\"[[Millennium (The X-Files)|Millennium]]\"\n|[[Thomas J. Wright]]\n|Vince Gilligan & [[Frank Spotnitz]]\n|November 28, 1999\n|7ABX05\n|15.09\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |147\n|7\n|8\n|\"[[The Amazing Maleeni]]\"\n|Thomas J. Wright\n|Vince Gilligan & [[John Shiban]] & Frank Spotnitz\n|January 16, 2000\n|7ABX08\n|16.18\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |149\n|7\n|10\n|\"[[Sein und Zeit (The X-Files)|Sein und Zeit]]\"\n|Michael Watkins\n|Chris Carter & Frank Spotnitz\n|February 6, 2000\n|7ABX10\n|13.95\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |150\n|7\n|11\n|\"[[Closure (The X-Files)|Closure]]\"\n|Kim Manners\n|Chris Carter & Frank Spotnitz\n|February 13, 2000\n|7ABX11\n|15.35\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |153\n|7\n|14\n|\"[[Theef]]\"\n|Kim Manners\n|Vince Gilligan & John Shiban & Frank Spotnitz\n|March 12, 2000\n|7ABX14\n|11.91\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |168\n|8\n|7\n|\"[[Via Negativa (The X-Files)|Via Negativa]]\"\n|[[Tony Wharmby]]\n|[[Frank Spotnitz]]\n|December 17, 2000\n|8ABX07\n|12.37\n|-\n! rowspan=\"1\" |172\n|8\n|11